parameters.name: ClientToken
parameters.description: Unique, case-sensitive identifier you provide to ensure the idempotency of the request. If you do not specify a client token, EventBridge Scheduler uses a randomly generated token for the request to ensure idempotency. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the schedule group that you are creating.

parameters.name: Tags
parameters.description: The list of tags to associate with the schedule group. (dict) --- Tag to associate with a schedule group. The key for the tag. The value for the tag.

nested_items.name: ScheduleGroupArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the schedule group.
